    "{\n",
    " \"cells\": [\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"# Tweet Topic Tracker\\n\",\"**NLP Project 71 of 100**\\n\",\"\\n\",\"## Project Overview\\n\",\"Group tweets by topic using TF-IDF + clustering and track topic trends over time.\\n\",\"\\n\",\"## Learning Objectives\\n\",\"1. Apply text clustering (K-Means, HDBSCAN) to social media data.\\n\",\"2. Use TF-IDF for tweet feature extraction.\\n\",\"3. Visualize topic trends over time.\\n\",\"4. Label clusters using top terms.\\n\",\"\\n\",\"## Problem Statement\\n\",\"Given a stream of tweets, automatically group them into topics and track volume over time.\\n\",\"\\n\",\"## Why This Matters\\n\",\"- Social media monitoring for brands and politics.\\n\",\"- Trend detection for news and crisis response.\\n\",\"- Understanding public discourse at scale.\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"## Dataset: Synthetic tweets.\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"import subprocess, sys, importlib\\nfor pkg in [\\\"pandas\\\",\\\"numpy\\\",\\\"matplotlib\\\",\\\"seaborn\\\",\\\"scikit-learn\\\"]:\\n    try: importlib.import_module(pkg)\\n    except ImportError: subprocess.check_call([sys.executable,\\\"-m\\\",\\\"pip\\\",\\\"install\\\",\\\"-q\\\",pkg])\\nprint('Ready.')\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"import numpy as np, pandas as pd, matplotlib.pyplot as plt, seaborn as sns\\nimport warnings; warnings.filterwarnings('ignore')\\nsns.set_style('whitegrid')\\n%matplotlib inline\\nfrom sklearn.feature_extraction.text import TfidfVectorizer\\nfrom sklearn.cluster import KMeans\\nfrom sklearn.decomposition import PCA\\nprint('Loaded.')\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"SEED = 42; rng = np.random.default_rng(SEED)\\n\\ntopics = {\\n    'Tech': ['AI is transforming everything','New iPhone release date announced','Tesla stock surges after earnings','OpenAI launches new model','Google announces quantum breakthrough'],\\n    'Sports': ['Lakers win championship','World Cup final was incredible','Messi scores hat trick','Olympics opening ceremony','NFL draft picks announced'],\\n    'Politics': ['Election results are in','New policy on climate change','Senate passes infrastructure bill','President addresses the nation','Trade deal negotiations continue'],\\n    'Entertainment': ['New Marvel movie breaks records','Grammy awards highlights','Netflix releases new series','Concert tickets sold out','Celebrity wedding announcement'],\\n}\\n\\nrows = []\\nfor _ in range(2000):\\n    topic = rng.choice(list(topics.keys()))\\n    base = rng.choice(topics[topic])\\n    noise = rng.choice(['wow','amazing','breaking','just heard','update','incredible','shocking'])\\n    date = pd.Timestamp('2025-01-01') + pd.Timedelta(days=int(rng.integers(0,180)))\\n    rows.append({'text': f'{noise} {base}'.lower(), 'date': date, 'true_topic': topic})\\n\\ndf = pd.DataFrame(rows).sort_values('date').reset_index(drop=True)\\nprint(f'Shape: {df.shape}'); print(df['true_topic'].value_counts()); df.head()\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"## Clustering\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"tfidf = TfidfVectorizer(max_features=3000, stop_words='english', ngram_range=(1,2))\\nX = tfidf.fit_transform(df['text'])\\n\\nkm = KMeans(n_clusters=4, random_state=SEED, n_init=10)\\ndf['cluster'] = km.fit_predict(X)\\n\\n# Label clusters by top terms\\nterms = tfidf.get_feature_names_out()\\nfor i in range(4):\\n    center = km.cluster_centers_[i]\\n    top_terms = [terms[j] for j in center.argsort()[-5:][::-1]]\\n    print(f'Cluster {i}: {top_terms}')\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"# PCA visualization\\npca = PCA(n_components=2, random_state=SEED)\\ncoords = pca.fit_transform(X.toarray())\\ndf['x'] = coords[:,0]; df['y'] = coords[:,1]\\n\\nfig, axes = plt.subplots(1,2,figsize=(14,5))\\nfor c in range(4):\\n    mask = df['cluster']==c\\n    axes[0].scatter(df.loc[mask,'x'], df.loc[mask,'y'], alpha=0.5, label=f'Cluster {c}', s=10)\\naxes[0].set_title('Clusters (PCA)'); axes[0].legend()\\n\\n# Topic trend over time\\ndf['month'] = df['date'].dt.to_period('M').astype(str)\\ndf.groupby(['month','cluster']).size().unstack(fill_value=0).plot(ax=axes[1])\\naxes[1].set_title('Topic Volume Over Time'); axes[1].tick_params(axis='x',rotation=45)\\nplt.tight_layout(); plt.show()\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"## Summary\\n\",\"- **TF-IDF + K-Means effectively groups tweets by topic.**\\n\",\"- **Top terms per cluster provide interpretable labels.**\\n\",\"- **Time-series view reveals topic trends and spikes.**\\n\",\"- **For production, use streaming clustering and real-time dashboards.**\"]}\n",
    " ],\n",
